        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Computes the chosen index based on the preferred index and a list of local minima. If the list of local minima is empty, the preferred index is returned. Otherwise, the index with the smallest value in the local minima list is returned.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>preferredIndex</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The preferred index. </para>
