<parameterdescription>
<para>A vector of pairs representing the local minima, where the first element is the index and the second element is the value. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The chosen index. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
